name: Bronze Conqueror Cannon
description: This robust cannon boasts a Bronze Frame, a symbol of resilience and the raw power that kicks off your NFT journey. Perfect for collectors ready to make a big bang.

name: Silver Conqueror Cannon
description: Encased in a gleaming Silver Frame, this cannon unleashes precision firepower. A step up from bronze, it's ideal for collectors seeking to expand their digital arsenal.

name: Gold Conqueror Cannon
description: This magnificent cannon, adorned with a Gold Frame, radiates power and prestige. A trophy for any collector seeking to dominate the battlefield and showcase their refined taste.

name: Emerald Conqueror Cannon
description: Enveloped in a radiant Emerald Frame, this cannon is a rare gem. Its vibrant green hue embodies explosive growth and unstoppable force, making it a standout addition to any collection.

name: Diamond Conqueror Cannon
description: Framed with dazzling Diamonds, this cannon is a force of unmatched brilliance. Its cutting-edge design makes it a coveted weapon for the most discerning collectors.

name: Master Conqueror Cannon
description: This cannon, enshrined in a Master Frame, embodies mastery of the battlefield. It's a testament to the collector's expertise and relentless pursuit of victory in the NFT arena.

name: Grandmaster Conqueror Cannon
description: Crafted with a Grandmaster Frame, this cannon represents unparalleled achievement. Its imposing presence signifies the collector's reign supreme in the NFT arena, a true champion's trophy.

name: Challenger Conqueror Cannon
description: Forged in a Challenger Frame, this cannon ignites the spirit of conquest. Its dynamic design signifies the collector's unwavering pursuit of victory, a weapon for those who leave their mark on the battlefield.

name: Legendary Conqueror Cannon
description: Woven with the essence of legend, this Legendary Frame imbues the cannon with mythical power. A coveted symbol of triumph, it signifies the collector's place among the NFT legends.
